    "macroSummary": "Markets are caught between escalating US-Iran tensions driving safe haven demand for USD/oil and ceasefire hopes providing relief rallies in risk assets. The geopolitical binary is creating whipsaw price action with crypto leading risk-on moves while traditional commodities reflect supply disruption fears. Oil volatility around $100+ and rising 10Y yields suggest stagflationary pressures are building ahead of the April 2 tariff deadline.",
